name: FigJam Calendar 2022
description:
Organize your and/or your team's day with FigJam Calendar! 📆


Set a clear guide on how to achieve specific to-dos and goals. Whether you are working from home, or you are back in the office I hope this calendar will help you!


I have included an example of an idea of how this calendar can be used in the team but you can use it as you wish - there are no rules.


Stay safe and keep being organized 📝
